Author contributions
L.D. and N.D. proposed the research and did the project planning. A.C. provided the
samples. E.B., A.C., and M.B. selected the single crystals. A.C., E.B., M.B., and L.D.
prepared the high-pressure experiments. E.B., M.B., A.C., L.D., H.-P.L., M.H., V.P., and
C.P., conducted single-crystal X-ray diffraction experiments. E.B. and M.B. analyzed the
single-crystal X-ray diffraction data. I.A.A. planned and supervised theoretical calcula-
tions. J.T., O.H., S.I.S., M.Be., and I.A.A. conducted ab initio calculations. E.B., M.B., L.D.,
N.D., and I.A.A. interpreted the results. E.B. and L.D. wrote the paper with contributions
of all authors.
